Two of the five patients are listed in critical condition; the other\u2019s conditions are undetermined at this time.\n\nA special phone number has been established for family inquiries:  1-888-394-4947.\n\nThe Blood Donation Center will open 8 a.m., to allow area residents to come in and donate. Donors can get to the Blood Donation Center by coming in the main hospital entrance at 2401 S. 31st Street, Temple.\n\nAs the Level 1 trauma center for the region, Scott & White Hospital \u2013 Temple is communicating and coordinating with emergency management out of Waco to provide care for victims.\n\nAnother update will follow."}
